metadata.name: Super Early Bulldogs #1
metadata.description: Super Early Bulldogs is an exclusive gaming pass of 1000 bulldogs, that will get you access to the bulldog metaverse, that will be part of the https://zudatopia.com metaverse. The zudatopia metaverse is already live, the bulldog land / world is not up yet. These dogs love to have fun, are adventerous, and have a great time. There are those who wear the crowns of a king, those who like to party. Could some of these traits mean something? We will find out!
